                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " In order to find any systematic errors in",
                "counting, a 239Pu foil and a 235U foil were compared",
                "under conditions obtained by separately interchanging",
                "scalars, amplifiers, and foils, and by moving the",
                "chamber within the block. No significant change in",
                "the counting ratio were detected. No further details",
                "on how the given uncertainty was determined."
              ]
